22
00:02:16,330 --> 00:02:17,659
SPEAKER_20: Chunsheng.

23
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:29,840
SPEAKER_20: I've run up a pile of debts lately.

62
00:07:17,029 --> 00:07:18,319
SPEAKER_20: You're up.

63
00:07:28,509 --> 00:07:29,970
SPEAKER_20: What's wrong?

91
00:09:44,379 --> 00:09:48,870
SPEAKER_20: Mr. Long'er says
if you're busy he'll take a rain check.

256
00:29:14,740 --> 00:29:16,769
SPEAKER_20: Might never go home again.

257
00:29:27,259 --> 00:29:29,220
SPEAKER_20: What are you looking at?

258
00:29:31,089 --> 00:29:32,890
SPEAKER_20: Thinking of escaping?

259
00:29:34,359 --> 00:29:37,130
SPEAKER_20: The Nationalists will shoot you.

268
00:30:41,029 --> 00:30:43,619
SPEAKER_20: I'd die happy if I could drive.

291
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:53,089
SPEAKER_20: Lao Quan, have a drink.

304
00:34:04,029 --> 00:34:05,130
SPEAKER_20: What?

305
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:11,340
SPEAKER_20: - Shouldn't we run, too?
- Where to?

324
00:35:19,739 --> 00:35:22,940
SPEAKER_20: - The attack hasn't started.
- Let's put them down.

672
01:18:49,890 --> 01:18:51,609
SPEAKER_20: It's me, Chunsheng.

673
01:18:59,500 --> 01:19:01,159
SPEAKER_20: I meant to call...

676
01:19:09,710 --> 01:19:11,699
SPEAKER_20: how could it be your son?

686
01:19:57,550 --> 01:19:59,489
SPEAKER_20: Take this for now.

687
01:20:02,159 --> 01:20:03,520
SPEAKER_20: It's money.

688
01:20:04,859 --> 01:20:07,520
SPEAKER_20: Tell me what else I can do.

702
01:20:56,909 --> 01:20:58,539
SPEAKER_20: I owe you a life.

703
01:21:01,149 --> 01:21:02,739
SPEAKER_20: I will remember.

704
01:21:12,090 --> 01:21:16,000
SPEAKER_20: What are you doing, you little wretch?
I'll teach you a lesson!

780
01:28:19,590 --> 01:28:20,920
SPEAKER_20: I'll be going.

873
01:37:43,579 --> 01:37:45,880
SPEAKER_20: Congratulations on Fengxia's wedding.

874
01:37:46,289 --> 01:37:48,760
SPEAKER_20: - When did you get here?
- A while ago.

875
01:37:49,090 --> 01:37:52,149
SPEAKER_20: But there were so many people,
I didn't come in.

889
01:39:01,430 --> 01:39:03,260
SPEAKER_20: I'll be going.

891
01:39:05,899 --> 01:39:07,270
SPEAKER_20: Never mind.

892
01:39:09,939 --> 01:39:12,739
SPEAKER_20: Jiazhen, I know you don't want to see me.

893
01:39:13,170 --> 01:39:15,800
SPEAKER_20: I'll leave my gift here and be gone.

950
01:44:06,270 --> 01:44:07,430
SPEAKER_20: Fugui!

951
01:44:11,369 --> 01:44:12,770
SPEAKER_20: Who's there?

952
01:44:12,840 --> 01:44:14,210
SPEAKER_20: Chunsheng.

953
01:44:15,539 --> 01:44:16,640
SPEAKER_20: Who?

954
01:44:16,710 --> 01:44:18,039
SPEAKER_20: Chunsheng.

955
01:44:23,149 --> 01:44:24,779
SPEAKER_20: What do you want?

956
01:44:26,949 --> 01:44:28,850
SPEAKER_20: Come out for a second.

959
01:45:08,359 --> 01:45:09,489
SPEAKER_20: Well?

960
01:45:10,100 --> 01:45:11,329
SPEAKER_20: Fugui...

961
01:45:12,329 --> 01:45:15,060
SPEAKER_20: I've always felt terrible about Youqing.

962
01:45:17,340 --> 01:45:21,300
SPEAKER_20: I've often tried to give you money.
You'd never accept it.

963
01:45:23,180 --> 01:45:26,310
SPEAKER_20: It's all in this account. Take it.

965
01:45:33,390 --> 01:45:34,819
SPEAKER_20: Take this...

966
01:45:36,220 --> 01:45:38,420
SPEAKER_20: and my heart will be at ease.

969
01:45:47,529 --> 01:45:49,869
SPEAKER_20: Yesterday, my wife killed herself.

974
01:46:01,279 --> 01:46:02,340
SPEAKER_20: No.

975
01:46:03,720 --> 01:46:05,979
SPEAKER_20: I just got an official notice.

990
01:47:11,619 --> 01:47:13,449
SPEAKER_20: I don't think I can.

993
01:47:25,170 --> 01:47:26,659
SPEAKER_20: Yes, come in.

994
01:47:26,970 --> 01:47:29,199
SPEAKER_20: No, thank you, I've got to go.

995
01:47:30,100 --> 01:47:32,039
SPEAKER_20: I snuck out just now...

996
01:47:32,109 --> 01:47:33,899
SPEAKER_20: and better get back.

997
01:47:41,380 --> 01:47:44,350
SPEAKER_20: Chunsheng, remember...

